0:13:08.26,000 --> 0:13:11,000
Think about the thousands and thousands of people who died

339
0:13:11.26,000 --> 0:13:14,000
trying to find the Northwest Passage.

340
0:13:14.26,000 --> 0:13:16,000
Well, the Northwest Passage is already there.

341
0:13:16.26,000 --> 0:13:18,000
I think it's sort of funny;

342
0:13:18.26,000 --> 0:13:2,000
it's on the Siberian coast,

343
0:13:20.26,000 --> 0:13:23,000
maybe the Russians will charge tolls.

344
0:13:23.26,000 --> 0:13:25,000
The governments of the world

345
0:13:25.26,000 --> 0:13:27,000
are taking this really seriously.

346
0:13:27.26,000 --> 0:13:3,000
The military of the Arctic nations

347
0:13:30.26,000 --> 0:13:33,000
is taking it really seriously.

348
0:13:33.26,000 --> 0:13:35,000
For all the denial of climate change

349
0:13:35.26,000 --> 0:13:37,000
by government leaders,

350
0:13:37.26,000 --> 0:13:39,000
the CIA

351
0:13:39.26,000 --> 0:13:41,000
and the navies of Norway

