412
0:16:03.26,000 --> 0:16:05,000
Well, there won't be any fish

413
0:16:05.26,000 --> 0:16:07,000
except for minnows,

414
0:16:07.26,000 --> 0:16:1,000
and the water will be pretty dirty,

415
0:16:10.26,000 --> 0:16:12,000
and all those kinds of things

416
0:16:12.26,000 --> 0:16:15,000
and full of mercury, etc., etc.

417
0:16:17.26,000 --> 0:16:19,000
And dead zones will get bigger and bigger

418
0:16:19.26,000 --> 0:16:21,000
and they'll start to merge,

419
0:16:21.26,000 --> 0:16:23,000
and we can imagine something like

420
0:16:23.26,000 --> 0:16:25,000
the dead-zonification

421
0:16:25.26,000 --> 0:16:28,000
of the global, coastal ocean.

